quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  5,51,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETTEHIDHUL-JEHUDE WE EN-NESARA ‘EWLIJA’E BA’DUHUM ‘EWLIJA’U BA’DIN WE MEN JETEWELLEHUM MINKUM FE’INNEHU MINHUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE
  5,52,FETERAL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN JUSARI’UNE FIHIM JEKULUNE NEHSHA ‘EN TUSIBENA DA’IRETUN FE’ASALLAHU ‘EN JE’TIJE BIL-FETHI ‘EW ‘EMRIN MIN ‘INDIHI FEJUSBIHU ‘ALA MA ‘ESERRU FI ‘ENFUSIHIM NADIMINE
  5,53,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘EHA’UULA’L-LEDHINE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM ‘INNEHUM LEME’AKUM HEBITET ‘A’MALUHUM FE’ESBEHU HASIRINE
  5,54,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU MEN JERTEDDE MINKUM ‘AN DINIHI FESEWFE JE’TI ELLAHU BIKAWMIN JUHIBBUHUM WE JUHIBBUNEHU ‘EDHILLETIN ‘ALEL-MU’UMININE ‘A’IZZETIN ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE JUXHAHIDUNE FI SEBILI ELLAHI WE LA JEHAFUNE LEWMETE LA’IMIN DHALIKE FEDLU ELLAHI JU’UT
  5,55,‘INNEMA WE LIJUKUMU ELLAHU WE RESULUHU WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENUL-LEDHINE JUKIMUNE ES-SELÆTE WE JU’UTUNE EZ-ZEKÆTE WE HUM RAKI’UNE
  5,56,WE MEN JETEWELLEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU FE’INNE HIZBEL-LAHI HUMUL-GALIBUNE
  5,57,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETTEHIDHUL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU DINEKUM HUZUEN WE LA’IBÆN MINEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE MIN KABLIKUM WEL-KUFFARE ‘EWLIJA’E WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  5,58,WE ‘IDHA NADEJTUM ‘ILA ES-SELÆTI ETTEHADHUHA HUZUEN WE LA’IBÆN DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KAWMUN LA JA’KILUNE
  5,59,KUL JA ‘EHLEL-KITABI HEL TENKIMUNE MINNA ‘ILLA ‘EN ‘AMENNA BILLAHI WE MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJNA WE MA ‘UNZILE MIN KABLU WE ‘ENNE ‘EKTHEREKUM FASIKUNE
  5,60,KUL HEL ‘UNEBBI’UKUM BISHERRIN MIN DHALIKE METHUBETEN ‘INDEL-LAHI MEN LE’ANEHU ELLAHU WE GADIBE ‘ALEJHI WE XHE’ALE MINHUMUL-KIREDETE WEL-HANAZIRE WE ‘ABEDET-TAGUTE ‘ULA’IKE SHERRUN MEKANÆN WE ‘EDELLU ‘AN SEWA’I ES-SEBILI
  5,61,WE ‘IDHA XHA’UKUM KALU ‘AMENNA WE KAD DEHALU BIL-KUFRI WE HUM KAD HAREXHU BIHI WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA KANU JEKTUMUNE
  5,62,WE TERA KETHIRÆN MINHUM JUSARI’UNE FIL-’ITHMI WEL-’UDWANI WE ‘EKLIHIMU ES-SUHTE LEBI’SE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  5,63,LEWLA JENHAHUMU ER-REBBANIJUNE WEL-’EHBARU ‘AN KAWLIHIMUL-’ITHME WE ‘EKLIHIMU ES-SUHTE LEBI’SE MA KANU JESNA’UNE
  5,64,WE KALETIL-JEHUDU JEDU ELLAHI MEGLULETUN GULLET ‘EJDIHIM WE LU’INU BIMA KALU BEL JEDAHU MEBSUTETANI JUNFIKU KEJFE JESHA’U WE LEJEZIDENNE KETHIRÆN MINHUM MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKE TUGJANÆN WE KUFRÆN WE ‘ELKAJNA BEJNEHUMUL-’ADAWETE WEL-BEGDA’E ‘ILA JEW
  5,65,WE LEW ‘ENNE ‘EHLEL-KITABI ‘AMENU WE ETTEKAW LEKEFFERNA ‘ANHUM SEJJI’ATIHIM WE LE’EDHALNAHUM XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  5,66,WE LEW ‘ENNEHUM ‘EKAMUT-TEWRÆTE WEL-’INXHILE WE MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJHIM MIN RABBIHIM LE’EKELU MIN FEWKIHIM WE MIN TEHTI ‘ERXHULIHIM MINHUM ‘UMMETUN MUKTESIDETUN WE KETHIRUN MINHUM SA’E MA JA’MELUNE